<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home Page</title>

    <style>
        /* Basic reset for margin and padding */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-image: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/531880/pexels-photo-531880.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-pixabay-531880.jpg&fm=jpg'); /* Replace with your actual background image URL */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }

        /* Header Styling */
        h1 {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Transparent black background to make text readable */
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Navigation Bar Styling */
        nav {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); /* Transparent dark background */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 15px 0;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            margin: 0 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #5fbae9;
        }

        /* Main Content Section */
        .main-content {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); /* White background with some transparency */
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 900px;
        }

        .main-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.2em;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .main-content p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

       

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <h1>
        Welcome to Our Home Page!
    </h1>

    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/product">Product</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <div class="main-content">
        <h2>Discover Our Products</h2>
        <p>Welcome to our website. Here, you'll find a variety of products that suit your needs. Whether you're looking for the latest technology, fashion, or home goods, we have something for everyone. Browse through our categories and make your purchase today!</p>
        <p>Feel free to explore our product catalog and contact us if you need any assistance. We are here to help!</p>
    </div>

  

</body>
</html>
